title: 20. Do I really I do all the things? How I get help to save my sanity!
description:
I am not a super mom, my friends. In this episode I'm sharing how I get help to get everything I need to get done- homeschooling the kids, cooking from scratch and running a business. 

Get my free 10 day course on how to start a blog here- https://pages.convertkit.com/fc79cda297/8d1e80f41d
